node.accessibility_caption: Photo by DeWayne Colley on July 14, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, child and indoor.

node.text: How it started vs how it’s going! In this first picture I was 17 with my first born son. I was broke financially but rich spiritually. But in the second picture I’m 33 and he is turning 16! God will speak through your story more than your mouth! #God #Jesusispoppin #Jesusbeenpoppin #kountrywayne #lethatsizzleinyourspirit #helpisontheway #love
